36:51.900 --> 36:54.260
Perhaps it was 1949, but it was around that time.

36:54.900 --> 36:57.820
Then, I don't know how you say it, is it Jorn Nieburg?

36:59.080 --> 37:00.040
Jorn Nyberg.

